Honestly i'm usually not fond of rewrite or replacement for old articles but this one is spot on.

I didn't really like the old Shapey, first it was kind of dull, didn't seem to be for children, and had no connection with the other mister. Not only is this version better, but makes a pretty good mister on his own. It's fun for kids (a shapeshifting person you can look like whoever you want), but it add something to the Little Mister lore with his job with Wondertainment. It's even way better executed than M.Hot who is only defined by his ability to find  things which makes him dull as a Mister.

And finally, the three  of other misters you're showing are good concepts on their own.

Great job !







